---
By: Papa Ramdas
Locus:
  Page: 263
  Verse: 10
Tags:
  - Elusions
---
Ignorance or delusion. ...sets us on the belief that this body of ours is
real and makes us forget the all-pervading Divine being whi is the one and
only reality. Living in this ignorance, our sole outlook on life becomes
one continued service of this unral and perishable body
